description: A special little couple are invited to 'backstage passes' at Fredbear's Family Diner, to meet the owner, William Afton! The whimsical man is giving them a tour of the goings-on behind the scenes, when Boyfriend challenges him to a rap battle. If he wins, he and GF get free pizzas for a whole year! Afton thinks on it, but who is he to deny such a challenge?
